  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网场景设计一个状态机，核心是IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream的追踪流程。初始状态是Absent，设备首次扫描\"Start\"后进入CheckedIn状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Start"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Absent到CheckedIn是扫描\"Start\"触发的。那如果设备在Absent时扫描了\"End\"呢？这种情况需要处理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这是个边界情况，应该进入Error状态，而且需要记录是由IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController触发的。另外CheckedIn之后扫描\"End\"会进入Attended状态，表示设备已被处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "Error",
        "End",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Absent到Error的转移，标注了ActuatorController。CheckedIn到Attended也连上了。那CheckedIn状态下如果再次扫描\"Start\"呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Start",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CheckedIn状态允许重复扫描\"Start\"，这时候还是TelemetryStream触发的，状态保持CheckedIn不变。Attended之后也是类似的自循环逻辑，但\"Start\"和\"End\"都可以触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Start",
        "End",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加CheckedIn的自循环和Attended的自循环。Error状态需要能恢复吗？还是终止状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Absent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Error不是终止状态，需要支持\"Сброс / Очистка ошибка\"操作回到Absent。另外给Error加个注释，说明这是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode检测到的无效操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Absent",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成。Error到Absent的恢复路径已添加，右侧注释也标注了EdgeNode的角色。整个状态流转：从TelemetryStream初始化进入Absent，经Start到CheckedIn，End到Attended，异常走Error可复位。",
